### Create a new entity
POST http://localhost:8090/restapi/countries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "AB",
  "countryName": "Alberta",
  "regionId": 10
}

### GET All entity from REST API endpoint
GET http://localhost:8090/restapi/countries

### GET One entity from REST API endpoint
GET http://localhost:8090/restapi/countries/AB

### UPDATE entity at the REST API endpoint - will replace all properties with the properties in the request body
PUT http://localhost:8090/restapi/countries/AB
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": "AB",
  "countryName": "New Alberta",
  "regionId": 20
}

### DELETE entity at the REST API endpoint
DELETE http://localhost:8090/restapi/countries/AB
